- Added minimal paragraph breaks/newline separation at a few dense transitions and before section headers to improve markdown readability/rendering.
- Fixed one malformed quote escape (`"officially\"` -> `"officially"`).
- Kept all math/LaTeX expressions unchanged.
- No duplicate abstract found in the body, so none removed.
